ISLAMABAD, Jan 30 (APP): Prime Minister Imran Khan Sunday appreciated GO petroleum for responding to his call and agreeing to give a 50 percent salary increase to its employees.
In a tweet on social media platform Twitter, he said, “I appreciate GO petroleum for responding to my call & agreeing to give a 50% salary increase to their employees. I am urging other companies to follow this example.”
